and then after that if I go...

03:48.103 --> 03:50.063
- No, no, no.
Kev, it's too late to apologize.

03:50.147 --> 03:52.149
The studio already removed you
from the fucking billboard.

03:52.232 --> 03:54.776
- So I'm done? Just like that, I'm done?

03:54.860 --> 03:56.195
- Maybe not.

03:56.278 --> 04:01.116
Claude Van De Velde wants
to meet with you.

04:03.452 --> 04:06.205
- Claude Van De Velde?
You're talking about the director?

04:06.288 --> 04:08.040
- Yes. Claude Van De Velde,

04:08.123 --> 04:10.083
director of four
of the six biggest action movies

04:10.167 --> 04:14.796
of all time,
saw the interview and wants to meet.

04:14.880 --> 04:16.298
- Why? What-what...?

04:16.381 --> 04:17.925
You know what? It don't matter.

04:18.008 --> 04:20.636
It d... It doesn't even fucking matter.
I'm there, okay?

04:20.719 --> 04:22.846
I'm there.

04:24.723 --> 04:26.433
Oh, shit.

04:33.273 --> 04:35.359
- I have seen all your films.

04:35.442 --> 04:38.779
I like all your films, but you, Kevin--

04:38.862 --> 04:41.281
you don't like your films.
- Wow, you can tell, huh?

04:41.365 --> 04:43.283
- Of course I can tell.

04:43.367 --> 04:46.328
You and I-- we are the same.

04:46.411 --> 04:48.956
My movies have grossed
billions of dollars.

04:49.039 --> 04:51.166
- Mm.
- Who cares?

04:51.250 --> 04:53.585
- Yeah, I mean,
it's not about the money, right?

04:53.669 --> 04:58.549
- It is about finding yourself
inside an artistic expression.

04:58.632 --> 05:00.050
- Yes.

05:00.133 --> 05:02.302
- I want to find you, Kevin.

05:03.262 --> 05:05.222
Will you let me find you?

05:05.305 --> 05:08.433
- You found me. I'm right here, man.

05:08.517 --> 05:13.146
- My next project is a serious,
gritty action film.

05:13.230 --> 05:16.859
