05:22.489 --> 05:24.783
- Holy shit, man. You got to be...
- Oh.

05:24.867 --> 05:26.201
- Excuse you.

05:26.285 --> 05:27.870
Watch it, man.
- My apologies, sir.

05:27.953 --> 05:30.622
- Mark Wahlberg would not scream
at a party server.

05:30.706 --> 05:32.875
- Oh, I didn't scream.
I didn't... I didn't scream...

05:32.958 --> 05:35.294
- An action star is tough, confident,

05:35.377 --> 05:40.257
