revered around the world.

06:18.337 --> 06:22.424
- Look, with all due respect,
I don't need that.

06:22.508 --> 06:24.510
I don't, I don't need none of that.

06:24.593 --> 06:25.928
I'm ready now.

06:26.011 --> 06:29.181
I'm ready right now.

06:29.264 --> 06:30.807
- Down here, Kevin.

06:30.891 --> 06:33.977
You don't think you need training,

06:34.061 --> 06:36.313
you want the part right now.

06:36.396 --> 06:41.151
Well, your new part is waiting
for you on that rooftop.

06:44.279 --> 06:46.198
Go and get it!

06:59.086 --> 07:00.963
